doc:44cdad75f3ae a prov:Entity , schema:text ;
	prov:generatedAtTime "2026-04-20T13:11:42.828042Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	schema:position 13 ;
	schema:identifier "44cdad75f3ae" .
doc:MLLifecycle schema:description "The creation of an MLOps model faces the fundamental challenge of data quality and quantity. DL techniques require large volumes of relevant data for training, and their robustness is often questioned. Data engineers and data scientists invest significant time and resources in cleaning, labeling and preparing the data, with low data quality being a common problem."@en ;
	rdfs:label "MLOps Adoption Challenge: Integrating Data Science and Software Engineering Work"@en ;
	mlops:hasDataStrategy mlops:DataStrategy ;
	schema:description "Data scientists often lack the software engineering background necessary for the maintenance and evolution of AI solutions."@en ;
	rdfs:label "MLOps Adoption Challenge: Data Quality and Quantity"@en .
doc:ee51f0c1e82e a prov:Entity , schema:text ;
	prov:generatedAtTime "2026-04-20T13:11:42.828217Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	schema:position 14 ;
	schema:identifier "ee51f0c1e82e" .
doc:FactsExpectationManagementChallenge schema:description "A lack of understanding of ML leads clients and managers to demand impossible results, such as a total absence of false positives or levels of accuracy that are unattainable with the available resources. There is a static view of model development, with no understanding of the need for continuous improvement and experimentation. Internally, data science teams often struggle to communicate the real limitations and potential of ML techniques to other project roles."@en .
doc:MLLifecycle rdfs:label "MLOps Adoption Benefit"@en .
doc:FactsExperimentalNatureChallenge schema:description "Building ML systems involves greater uncertainty and risk due to the management of trained data and models. Practices such as managing experiments and testing multiple hypotheses are critical, reflecting an iterative and exploratory process to achieve desired goals. This experimental nature contributes to ML projects being more prone to failure, and organizations are often in the early stages of adopting practices to manage them effectively."@en .
doc:MLLifecycle rdfs:label "ML Lifecycle Challenge"@en ;
	schema:description "Traditional software engineering patterns and practices do not always fit the unique needs of data science, such as data management and model drifting."@en ;
	mlops:hasChallenge mlops:MLPrivacy .
doc:FactsExperimentalNatureChallenge a mlops:MLChallenge .
doc:MLLifecycle rdfs:label "Data Privacy Challenge"@en ;
	mlops:hasChallenge mlops:MLResourceConstraint .
doc:FactsExpectationManagementChallenge rdfs:label "Unrealistic Expectations Challenge"@en .
doc:MLLifecycle schema:description "Adoption of MLOps optimizes the ML product lifecycle by addressing challenges such as data management, model drifting, and multidisciplinary collaboration."@en .
doc:FactsExpectationManagementChallenge a mlops:MLChallenge .
doc:MLLifecycle rdfs:label "ML Product Lifecycle Challenge"@en ;
	schema:description "It is critical to establish and manage customer privacy information from project conception."@en , "The high cost of specialized hardware such as GPUs, and infrastructure hinders the implementation of ML especially for small and medium enterprises when considering the expected return on investment (ROI). The cloud plays a key role by not requiring the purchase of expensive and specialized ML equipment, additionally highlighting the need for efficient resource management within MLOps practices and the exploration of less complex models in resource constrained environments."@en .
doc:FactsExpectationManagementChallenge mlops:hasChallenge mlops:ExpectationManagementChallenge .
doc:MLLifecycle schema:description "Lack of shared understanding about the complexity of the ML product lifecycle can negatively impact the delivery of successful ML systems."@en ;
	rdfs:label "Computational Resource Challenge"@en .
doc:FactsExperimentalNatureChallenge rdfs:label "Experimental Nature Challenge"@en ;
	mlops:hasChallenge mlops:ExperimentalNatureChallenge .
doc:MLLifecycle mlops:hasChallenge mlops:MLLifecycleChallenge .
